00:33:32,966 --> 00:33:36,229
Next, he looked at what people associate

528
00:33:36,229 --> 00:33:37,270
with those different colors,

529
00:33:37,270 --> 00:33:40,613
so that bright blue was associated with the sky,

530
00:33:40,613 --> 00:33:44,396
and that dirty yellow was associated with vomit.

